Singer Yvonne Chaka Chaka and hubby Dr Mandlalele Mhinga are celebrating more than three decades of marriage together. This is a milestone for the Princess of Africa, because showbiz marriages don't last this long. Taking to her Twitter account, she celebrated this milestone by thanking her hubby, saying, although 31 years is a long time to be with someone, she has enjoyed every single minute of their nuptials. "31 years is a long time, checked the marriage certificate can’t find the expiry date. God has been good. Thank you all." Read: DR DRE'S WIFE CHALLENGES PRENUP! 31 years is a long time checked the marriage certificate can’t find the expiry date .God is been Good .Thank u all ???? pic.twitter.com/0Wnwb9kbnH 